# Project Structure Guide

The main entry point is [src/main.rs](mdc:src/main.rs), which handles CLI argument parsing and program startup.

Provider integrations are located in [src/providers/](mdc:src/providers):
- [mod.rs](mdc:src/providers/mod.rs): Defines the Provider trait and factory logic.
- [openai.rs](mdc:src/providers/openai.rs): OpenAI GPT integration.
- [anthropic.rs](mdc:src/providers/anthropic.rs): Anthropic Claude integration.
- [google.rs](mdc:src/providers/google.rs): Google AI integration.
- [ollama.rs](mdc:src/providers/ollama.rs): Ollama local model integration.
